events.text: Ah, yes, the Horugaloos. See, in fanon, the Horugaloos are generally considered to be unpleasant. However, I think that this characterization is unfounded. Unjust, even!  After all, if it wasn't for the service of the Horugaloos, the entirety of the Space-Time-Horu continuum would be in utter shambles! I mean, just really torn to shreds. Completely destroyed. Totally ruined. Uninhabitable! Strangely, more green than you might expect. This text intentionally overflows.
Have you noticed that you say the brackets out loud?
